headline: Hormel Foods Named One of 60 Best Companies to Sell For - 24 Years Running
summary: For the 24th time, Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE: HRL), a Fortune 500 global branded food company, has made the Selling Power magazine's 60 Best Companies to Sell For 2025 list. The list recognizes 60 of the most deserving sales organizations in the United States.

headline: Hormel: An Undervalued Protein Market Leader
summary: Hormel offers strong brand leadership, a 59-year dividend growth streak, and nearly 4% yield at a decade high, despite challenges. Learn why HRL stock is a buy.
